@node Display time face
@section Display time face

The face @code{faces-extras-display-time} inherits from @code{bold} and is intended for the @code{display-time-string} when shown in the mode line or tab bar. It is used by the time element in @samp{tab-bar-extras.el} (@ref{Display time face}) to give the clock a visually distinct appearance.

